node.text:
Peloton's mission is to help people be the best version of themselves by making it easier to access world-class fitness and wellness content. Today, we’re taking another step towards making Peloton more accessible and attainable by lowering the price of the original Peloton Bike. Starting today, the original Peloton Bike will be available in the U.S., U.K., Canada, Germany, and Australia starting at $39 USD a month ($49 CAD/month, £35 GBP/month, €39 EUR/month; All-Access Membership Separate).

We’re also making it easier to access the Peloton Bike+ and the new Peloton Tread by extending our financing terms, helping to lower monthly payments for qualified customers. Learn more about how we’re making it easier to become part of the Peloton community by tapping this image at the link in our bio.
